---
const contacts = [
  { label: "Email", value: "hello@drkooo.com", href: "mailto:hello@drkooo.com" },
  { label: "GitHub", value: "github.com/drkooo", href: "https://github.com/drkooo" },
  { label: "CubeCut Demo", value: "cube.drkooo.com", href: "https://cube.drkooo.com", i18nLabel: "contact.cubecutDemo" },
];
---

<section id="contact" class="section bg-alt">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14 reveal">
      <span class="badge" data-i18n="contact.badge">Contact</span>
      <h2 class="section-title mt-4" data-i18n="contact.title">合作与沟通</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto" data-i18n="contact.subtitle">如果你正在做产品升级、品牌官网改版，或需要前端与交互落地支持，可以直接联系我。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-6">
      <article class="card p-7 reveal">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold" data-i18n="contact.preferenceTitle">沟通偏好</h3>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-secondary">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">01.</span><span data-i18n="contact.pref1">先对齐目标与边界，再拆分迭代计划。</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">02.</span><span data-i18n="contact.pref2">强调交付节奏和可维护实现，不做一次性“炫技页面”。</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent">03.</span><span data-i18n="contact.pref3">支持从设计细化到工程落地的协同闭环。</span></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="mailto:hello@drkooo.com" class="btn btn-primary" data-i18n="contact.emailBtn">发邮件咨询</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/drkooo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" data-i18n="contact.githubBtn">查看 GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card p-7 reveal">
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary" data-i18n="contact.directLinks">Direct Links</p>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          {contacts.map((item) => (
            <a href={item.href} target={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "_blank" : undefined} rel={item.href.startsWith("http") ? "noopener noreferrer" : undefined} class="block rounded-xl border border-primary bg-alt px-4 py-3 hover:border-[var(--accent)] transition-colors">
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary" data-i18n={item.i18nLabel}>{item.label}</p>
              <p class="mt-1 font-medium text-primary inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                {item.value}
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6h8m0 0v8m0-8-10 10" /></svg>
              </p>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-primary bg-alt px-4 py-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary" data-i18n="contact.response">Response</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm" data-i18n="contact.responseDesc">通常在 24 小时内回复。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
